org.jsonurl.stream

Class AbstractCharIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsonurl.stream.AbstractCharIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CharIterator, Resource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonUrlCharSequence

    public abstract class AbstractCharIterator
extends Object
implements CharIterator
    Provides the boilerplate for CharIterator implementations.

    This class provides buffering and offset/line/column counting. If you need to implement a new CharIterator then extending this will provide that basic functionality for you.

    Since:
    2020-11-01
    Author:
    jsonurl.org, David MacCormack
